# 🎓 Course Enrollment System

A full-stack Course Enrollment System built with:

- 🔧 **Backend**: Ruby on Rails 8 with Devise Token Auth & MySQL
- 🎨 **Frontend**: React (Vite) with Tailwind CSS
- 🔐 **Authentication**: Token-based login for Students, Instructors, and Admins

---

## 🚀 Features

- 👨‍🎓 Student registration (without password)
- 👩‍🏫 Instructor registration/login (with secret code)
- 🧑‍💼 Admin login to manage courses
- 📚 Browse and enroll in courses
- ✅ Prevent over-enrollment based on course capacity
- 👀 View enrolled courses
- 🗑️ Unenroll from courses
- 🧮 Real-time update of enrolled student count
- 🔐 Role-based access for Student, Instructor, Admin

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Stack | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Frontend | React, Tailwind CSS, React Router |
| Backend | Ruby on Rails 8, MySQL |
| Auth | Devise Token Auth |
| API | RESTful APIs with token headers |

